==English==

===Noun===
'''broth''' (''[[countable]] and [[uncountable]]; plural'' '''broths''')

#<!--DefA-->(''uncountable'') [[Water]] in which food ([[meat]] or [[vegetable]] etc) has been [[boil]]ed.
#<!--DefB-->(''countable'') A [[soup]] made from broth and other [[ingredient]]s such as vegetables, herbs or diced meat.

====Synonyms====

* [[bouillon]]

